     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <pb facs="6"/>
   <pb facs="6"/>
   <head>To the freendly
Reader.</head>
   <p>
      <hi>
         <seg rend="decorInit">I</seg>T were needlesse gen<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>tle</hi>
Reader, to vse a
large preamble in
so breefe a purpose:
or to trifle the time
in tediousnes, when a woord
or twaine may suffise. It is a
custome, and I would be loth
to breake it, to desire thy freend<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ship,
in reading this little fan<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>cie:
which how farre it is from
any ill intent, so farre I wish
euill suspect may be from thy
minde. This is all my reque<gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="2 letters">
         <desc>••</desc>
      </gap>,
to read with aduise, rewarde
with gentlenes: and then take
thy choyse, either of Looue or
Learning.</p>
   <closer>
      <signed>Thy freend. <hi>A. Munday.</hi>
      </signed>
   </closer>
